In Crucible when a line that has a comment is removed in a new version of the file, that Comment or Defect doesn't show up in the current version of the file.

This along with no existing general comment thread information page makes it very difficult to track down and make sure comments and defects are addressed or to see comments without spending a lot of time hunting through the review.

To make Crucible a more usable tool it is strongly desired to have a way to be able to find comments more easily. (Something like a new page or view that lists or links all comment threads or at the very least lists the artifact and version so the comment can be found without stumbling through each revision of the file).

